# Muraz, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Muraz (; , Mora≈∫) is a rural locality (a village) in Imendyashevsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 124 as of 2010. There are 3 streets.
Geography
Muraz is located 51 km northeast of Krasnousolsky (the district's administrative centre) by road. Karagayevo is the nearest rural locality.
